{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"eb4c41b1f9","title":"开城工作今后交由朝鲜同志负责","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6bdae660a5","index":0,"year":1954,"month":11,"day":24,"articleId":"eb4c41b1f9"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"daf4a343f2","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eb4c41b1f9","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"惠司，即中国人民志愿军司令部。柴成文，当时任朝鲜军事停战委员会中国人民志愿军代表。"},{"id":"0bd4fd854e","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eb4c41b1f9","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李相朝，当时任朝鲜军事停战委员会朝中方面首席谈判代表。丁国钰，当时任朝鲜军事停战委员会中国人民志愿军代表团党委副书记。"}],"contents":[{"id":"77a5a7b3e6","type":"title","text":"开城工作今后交由朝鲜同志负责”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eb4c41b1f9"},{"id":"daf4a343f2","type":"paragraph","text":"金首相，并告志司","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eb4c41b1f9"},{"id":"0bd4fd854e","type":"paragraph","text":"过去由于谈判的需要，开城的工作一直由中国同志负较大部分的责任。在共同对外的斗争中，朝中同志都取得了若干经验，同时开城工作显然有长期化的超势。在这种情况下，升城工作今后交由朝鲜同志负责，由您直接领导较为适宜。我们也考虑过由朝鲜同志负责时的若十具体困难，但这些困难是可以采取相互协作的办法求得解决的。您如同意上述办法，当即派现在国内休假的柴成文同志来平向您报告并请示，然后去开城和李相朝、丁国钰二同志商量具体执行的办法","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eb4c41b1f9"},{"id":"89b4b04b0d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eb4c41b1f9"},{"id":"434a27f7b2","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五四年十一月二十四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eb4c41b1f9"},{"id":"8dd4286596","type":"paragraph","text":"[II这是毛泽东给朝鲜民主主义人民共和国首相金日成的电报。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eb4c41b1f9"}],"page":{"id":"a964e9e156","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"eb4c41b1f9","start":352,"end":352}}}},"__N_SSG":true}